Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近哥哥總一個人偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概 是因為女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 浴室空出來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,媽媽說讓你快去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:13.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:16.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼 密碼是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:18.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還在用入學考試的考號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真不小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川由紀 果然是這女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.02\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\move(386,292,350,180)}我是不是也差不多該\N去洗澡了呢（*‐*）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\frz17.86\move(458,482,432,392)}啊！剛才肯定在\N想奇怪的東西吧（¬_¬）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\fs35\c&H656363&\an1\frz16.52\move(780,500,758,412)}唔嗯唔嗯\N走好走好～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個誆騙哥哥的壞女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:28.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看我教訓你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 以後能別再和我說話了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,打擾我學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是小螢吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:42.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸…為什麼 我做了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說 是因為那件事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那件事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她做了什麼讓哥哥生氣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 挺像這女人做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:53.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但那件事不是古屋君你所渴求的嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,渴求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是借了筆記之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白總之先嗆回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼無聊的事情你給我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:07.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好過分!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:08.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我明明也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:09.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,第一次的說‥!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,第一次? 什麼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:17.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥所渴求的同時還是這女人的第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:19.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 難道說是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實這事情是我渴求的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是約個會而已大家都在做的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,況且對我而言也是第一次約會的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然 沒懂呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:31.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那那場約會只是在玩弄我嗎??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:35.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這段時間總是晚歸 果然是和這女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.39,0:02:41.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那和我睡覺也都是假的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,睡覺?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是一起睡過午覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,居然在約會的時候睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥也變奇怪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不過就睡了一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那肚子裡的孩子要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原來是這個意思啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但…但是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不做那種事的話就不會有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥這種人居然也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的是我的孩子嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你有證據嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我除了和古屋君以外的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒·再·睡·過·啊 {\c&H006A63ED}❤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,騙人的這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明 還只是高中生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:38.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你在我房裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,媽媽!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥他有孩子了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,螢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我和同班的女生開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,試著交往後 便有了想要珍惜她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 完全不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 和我在一起開心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 嗯很開心喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說實話我對這種事情很不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是有哪裡不滿意的別客氣儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 就說一點可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 並不是很重要的事情就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得自己明白剛田君的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還是想聽你說出來呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,「我喜歡你」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 這種事情很麻煩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 這點小事也還好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 為什麼要特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也覺得自己像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:45.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但就是想聽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了上根 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,確實可能我至今 都沒有好好的說出自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,以後我多注意一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我不是在說以後耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我誤會什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以的話現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢 現在就應該展現誠意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 不我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 有什麼想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…個 那…個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這次我們就一起去哪裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種叫法雖然很難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算做是…第一次約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是的 我不是想去約會!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:31.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:35.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我現在就只想聽剛田君你說喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為剛田君 你還一次都沒為我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:46.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然約會也很開心 但我還是想聽這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 突然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為這樣的話不過是我讓你說這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 我好像說了些任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說起來 剛才說要約會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 上根
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 我喜歡你!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然現在無論說什麼都好像是你讓我說的一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的 打從心底喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我應該早點說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都怪我太遲鈍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 臉全紅了喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:35.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近似乎總有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡在簡訊告白什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種人真的超爛的呢～（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:45.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是高瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:46.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,透過這種方式告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的感到很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但就是 喜歡高瀨你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為郵件發失敗了搞得很尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:02.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,神田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,由 小由紀 英語作業做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 有作業的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這絕對很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那之後的郵件也不知道她看沒看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要不再發一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不能靠郵件得親口說才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是她都不聽我說 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不自覺的很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,很在意是說 什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這個人嘴巴很笨拙可能說的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在的你跟以前的我一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個人怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在哪見過這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 跟你沒關係 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是女人吧 一看就知道了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說了吧 你跟我很像的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也把女人弄哭得很慘過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我倒沒有弄哭得那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但你還是弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,把最不想弄哭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找這個人商量的話說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你肯定以為我是戀愛達人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:17.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,戀愛? 咦? 在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到你我就會想起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個在雨中瑟瑟發抖的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:29.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你說怎麼樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對方都不跟我說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不知道 我是笨蛋所以完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,除了現在馬上跑過去緊緊抱住她之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:47.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總覺得 被這麼一說就想這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你還在這磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:56.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 謝謝你給我這麼寶貴的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,建議? 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:01.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我只是說了自己想說的話而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這不過是一個被稱作戀愛達人的人說的傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好了 快去吧 她要回去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊對了 最後能不能告訴我前輩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:24.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前 前輩!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:30.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最近總有點恍神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:31.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上課時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:34.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是回過神來就發現自己在看奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且 胸口還有點難受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小千 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你最近很奇怪耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 可能是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我腦中總是閃過菅原的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:00.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種事還是第一次 真的是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,心跳得厲害了 肯定感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 感覺有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 社團活動的時候稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,醫務室的老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛才出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:24.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 不去足球部不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在說什麼啊我這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣下去完全聊不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,腦袋本來就有點恍惚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,得考慮一下話題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:42.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 高野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不是來量體溫什麼的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對啊 果然可能是發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我回社團那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:06.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊不對 我是說我不知道體溫計在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}什麼嘛 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你這麼紅著臉跟我說 讓我有點心動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是吧 我的臉有這麼紅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}嘛 跟平時比起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不 但是不應該是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我懂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高野不懂談戀愛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:39.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這個是最新款好像五秒就能測出來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒發燒就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:43.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可是 如果沒有發燒的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}如果不是發燒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}正常體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然還是有點發燒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的嗎! 快點回家比較好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那我去社團那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:13.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}多保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:23.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是發燒的話 到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 滿身傷痕的天使
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的機率的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是跨不出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們的關係可以說是曖昧模糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然無聊但還是希望能感受到屬於我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要珍視這份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.98,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}振り返ればまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.24,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あの頃と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.82,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}熱を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:23.29,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君といつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:28.58,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}同じ思い出ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.67,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.84,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:41.35,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.18,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.64,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:53.03,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:58.45,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:05.00,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:10.17,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:16.05,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:22.14,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:11.98,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}回首仰望過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.24,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}依然同那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.82,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}感受著你的熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:23.29,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}無論何時同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:28.58,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}全都是同樣的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.67,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}逐漸淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.84,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:41.35,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}害怕這逐漸的  忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:44.18,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:46.64,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想把這份風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:53.03,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:58.45,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:05.00,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:10.17,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:16.05,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:22.14,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你能在我身旁而已
